overview: Henry is torn between two choices: to go after Cikgu Ayu or Sarah Jane. The gang decides to travel all the way to Terengganu to search for Cikgu Ayu but someone in the village plans to marry Cikgu Ayu. Will the gang succeed to foil the plans of the billionaire and bring Cikgu Ayu back to SMK Ayer Dalam?
title: Oh My English Ganu
